Yousef,

I tried to compile ITSOL_1 on my machine. It failed because of a typo
in 
      LIB/systimer.c

Here comes the solution :
---------------------------------
 #include <sys/time.h>

 #ifndef CLK_TCK
-#define ClK_TCK 100
+#define CLK_TCK 100
 #endif

 #ifndef CLOCKS_PER_SEC
---------------------------------

Thanks for working on ITSOL.

Kind regards
 Dominique

